cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with gesture recognition from videos using deep learning models. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a joint 3DCNN-LSTM model that is end-to-end trainable. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing a compact and accurate model for gesture recognition. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with recognizing gestures from videos. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the suitability of the final model for real-time gesture recognition on mobile devices, which is relevant to HCI.
